{"tid":1176623,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"就到30 一事無成","createTime":"2019-05-29T10:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-29T12:01:24.000Z","uid":9846,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac9ef737b12522c145b51b365b28e0f3330aaf6","tid":1176623,"uid":9846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:39:25.000Z","msg":"依家都28，過多兩年就到30，啲人話30先係一個男人嘅開始，應該步入穩重，應該更加成熟。<br />\n我依家月入30k左右，無女，無樓，無父幹。曾經嘅我，對未來充滿希望，以為自己係世界嘅主人公，故事嘅主角，出咗嚟社會先知自己嘅渺小，我諗人們所講30歲嘅成熟，其實係指我哋應該接受平凡。<br />\n平凡嘅我過著平凡嘅一生。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2b33bbf3f218e2be2a758fa1f1b72de9f40f7c","tid":1176623,"uid":13866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"草唔草到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a70fcf168cee31bdb7a54cbed2130f68e069955","tid":1176623,"uid":129138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:41:37.000Z","msg":"Bro, you are not alone"},{"pid":"df9627674aa3e30755b48d7176a5475f3abdf2ed","tid":1176623,"uid":86614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"有30k算係咁啦"},{"pid":"3a5d74d3f6247ae4474e867d6e3dcb881cb8caff","tid":1176623,"uid":175760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:48:02.000Z","msg":"6月9"},{"pid":"9efe874b504068ce8ca3ea0c69cd56b6cea4a15d","tid":1176623,"uid":73089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df9627674aa3e30755b48d7176a5475f3abdf2ed","tid":1176623,"uid":86614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:43:16.000Z","msg":"有30k算係咁啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-29T10:56:26.000Z","msg":"係囉 meet 到連登要求 人工跟歲數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未到30都30k"},{"pid":"aeeaec67b19b46528a2168b8f5cf1e2a0797d5a2","tid":1176623,"uid":9846